WEBVTT

1
00:00:22.439 --> 00:00:24.023
Covey! Cars are here. Let's go.

2
00:00:30.947 --> 00:00:33.324
I'll... I'll see you down there.

3
00:00:35.869 --> 00:00:37.661
- Hi.
- Uh. hi.

4
00:00:37.662 --> 00:00:40.873
Covey. what on earth was that?

5
00:00:40.874 --> 00:00:42.750
Oh. so you saw that?

6
00:00:42.751 --> 00:00:45.502
Since when
do you even like Yuri?

7
00:00:45.503 --> 00:00:47.171
Yesterday you were all about Praveena.

8
00:00:47.172 --> 00:00:51.926
Okay. the truth is. I started
having feelings for her last semester.

9
00:00:52.427 --> 00:00:55.137
It's... it's part of
why I broke up with Dae.

10
00:00:55.138 --> 00:00:58.182
So. when Dae almost punched me
in the face...?

11
00:00:58.183 --> 00:01:00.559
He knew that I had feelings
for somebody else.

12
00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:01.853
and he thought that it was you.

13
00:01:03.229 --> 00:01:04.813
What am I gonna do now?

14
00:01:04.814 --> 00:01:06.315
I need to talk to Yuri.

15
00:01:06.316 --> 00:01:08.484
What you do now is get to the cars.

16
00:01:08.485 --> 00:01:10.862
And try not to ruin my ski weekend.

17
00:01:12.197 --> 00:01:14.032
Right. Okay.

18
00:01:14.908 --> 00:01:15.950
Okay.

19
00:01:25.335 --> 00:01:27.044
I didn't think you'd come.

20
00:01:27.045 --> 00:01:28.838
Yeah. I know.

21
00:01:29.756 --> 00:01:31.048
We have a lot to talk about.

22
00:01:31.049 --> 00:01:34.384
Seollal ski weekend. baby!

23
00:01:34.385 --> 00:01:36.137
I don't think I can do this.

24
00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:38.431
Guess who!

25
00:01:39.099 --> 00:01:41.016
- Hey.
- Hi.

26
00:01:41.017 --> 00:01:43.978
Oh. I think Yuri and Juliana made up.
Should we ride with them?

27
00:01:46.439 --> 00:01:49.274
That one seems full.
Why don't you take this one?

28
00:01:49.275 --> 00:01:50.943
This weekend's gonna be so fun.

29
00:01:53.154 --> 00:01:56.198
- Thank you.
- Yep. It's gonna be one for the books.

30
00:02:16.511 --> 00:02:18.095
Wow.

31
00:02:18.096 --> 00:02:20.681
It's beautiful up here.

32
00:02:20.682 --> 00:02:22.976
Got to admit. I've missed this place.

33
00:02:23.476 --> 00:02:26.478
Hey. can we talk? I'm freaking out.

34
00:02:26.479 --> 00:02:28.480
Not right now. It's too risky.

35
00:02:32.443 --> 00:02:33.444
Eunice.

36
00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:35.738
Let me get that for you.

37
00:02:41.035 --> 00:02:43.370
What did you pack?
We're only here two days.

38
00:02:43.371 --> 00:02:45.915
I like to be prepared.

39
00:02:46.833 --> 00:02:48.585
For the apocalypse?

40
00:02:54.424 --> 00:02:55.257
Sorry.

41
00:02:55.258 --> 00:02:57.885
I'll clean it.
I'm sure it's expensive--

42
00:02:57.886 --> 00:03:00.512
Don't worry. it's a fake.

43
00:03:00.513 --> 00:03:01.889
But I thought you were rich.

44
00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:04.224
No. I'm not.

45
00:03:04.225 --> 00:03:08.896
- I live in the same neighborhood as you.
- Really?

46
00:03:08.897 --> 00:03:11.274
You really don't know me
at all.

47
00:03:13.443 --> 00:03:15.986
All right. Dad will be here
in a few hours.

48
00:03:15.987 --> 00:03:19.364
Tomorrow. we ski Alpensia
and have dinner by Baek Jong Won.

49
00:03:19.365 --> 00:03:20.991
- All right.
- Wow.

50
00:03:20.992 --> 00:03:23.952
All right. settle down. Come on in.
Make yourselves at home.

51
00:03:23.953 --> 00:03:25.078
Let's go!

52
00:03:25.079 --> 00:03:27.999
Korean Kris Jenner.

53
00:03:28.958 --> 00:03:32.711
- There's. like. no photos of you.
- Thanks for noticing. Madison.

54
00:03:32.712 --> 00:03:33.880
Wait. is this your brother?

55
00:03:34.714 --> 00:03:35.714
Half-brother.

56
00:03:35.715 --> 00:03:39.344
Joon Ho is Dad's firstborn.
and best-selling artist.

57
00:03:40.428 --> 00:03:41.638
Moving on.

58
00:03:42.472 --> 00:03:44.264
Oh my God.

59
00:03:44.265 --> 00:03:46.683
- Jump scare.
- Yeah.

60
00:03:46.684 --> 00:03:48.518
Talk about a full moon.

61
00:03:48.519 --> 00:03:50.772
Oh. speaking of...

62
00:03:55.526 --> 00:03:57.153
He's not coming.

63
00:03:57.654 --> 00:03:59.155
Min Ho. Uh...

64
00:04:00.865 --> 00:04:02.950
Since my dad decided to bail.

65
00:04:02.951 --> 00:04:05.327
some of the girls
can use the primary suite.

66
00:04:05.328 --> 00:04:08.914
The boys can take the back bedroom.
There's also a pullout in my dad's office.

67
00:04:08.915 --> 00:04:11.125
- He has an office here?
- Dibs.

68
00:04:12.001 --> 00:04:15.170
I... I need the single.
I'm a night screamer.

69
00:04:15.171 --> 00:04:16.588
- No. you're not.
- Fine.

70
00:04:16.589 --> 00:04:18.840
- It's bubble guts.
- Okay.

71
00:04:18.841 --> 00:04:20.342
Okay. none of you'd know this.

72
00:04:20.343 --> 00:04:23.637
but intense running
actually causes intense... runs.

73
00:04:23.638 --> 00:04:26.640
- Okay. spare us the deets. Room's yours.
- Okay.

74
00:04:26.641 --> 00:04:29.268
We should get to bed
if we're gonna hit the slopes early.

75
00:04:29.269 --> 00:04:30.353
Good night.

76
00:04:35.275 --> 00:04:36.526
Hey.

77
00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:41.614
You know. coming here was all his idea.

78
00:04:42.615 --> 00:04:45.994
But the second
precious Joon Ho is available.

79
00:04:47.578 --> 00:04:48.663
he drops me.

80
00:04:49.747 --> 00:04:51.456
He's never put me first.

81
00:04:51.457 --> 00:04:53.834
This... This must be really hard.

82
00:04:53.835 --> 00:04:55.169
I wish I didn't care.

83
00:04:55.670 --> 00:04:56.754
I get it.

84
00:04:57.547 --> 00:05:01.592
I mean. there have been plenty of times
when I felt like I'm not enough either.

85
00:05:05.179 --> 00:05:07.932
Doesn't church help with things like that?

86
00:05:10.977 --> 00:05:12.895
God can't fix everything. Min Ho.

87
00:05:13.771 --> 00:05:14.772
Really?

88
00:05:16.232 --> 00:05:17.983
I thought that was his whole deal.

89
00:05:19.485 --> 00:05:20.402
No?

90
00:05:23.489 --> 00:05:26.700
<i>Only a few hours ago.
Yuri and I were kissing.</i>

91
00:05:26.701 --> 00:05:29.036
<i>Is she thinking about it as much as I am?</i>

92
00:05:29.037 --> 00:05:30.413
Cool if I sleep here?

93
00:05:31.205 --> 00:05:34.167
Yeah. of course.
The more the merrier.

94
00:05:35.043 --> 00:05:37.377
This is giving
slumber party vibes.

95
00:05:37.378 --> 00:05:39.504
Who's gonna start the girl talk?

96
00:05:39.505 --> 00:05:41.590
We could play Never Have I Ever.

97
00:05:41.591 --> 00:05:43.050
Get to the real dirt.

98
00:05:43.051 --> 00:05:45.636
I'm really beat.

99
00:05:47.013 --> 00:05:51.016
I forgot to brush my teeth.
so I'm gonna go do that.

100
00:05:51.017 --> 00:05:52.893
Right now.

101
00:05:52.894 --> 00:05:54.895
Kitty. don't you need this?

102
00:05:56.689 --> 00:05:57.607
Thank you.

103
00:06:01.027 --> 00:06:03.528
- Hi. Thank God you got the single.
- Hey.

104
00:06:03.529 --> 00:06:05.156
I really need to tell you something.

105
00:06:05.907 --> 00:06:07.074
Yuri and I kissed.

106
00:06:07.075 --> 00:06:09.284
Huh? When?

107
00:06:09.285 --> 00:06:12.871
A few hours ago.
right after Juliana and her had a fight.

108
00:06:12.872 --> 00:06:16.291
I don't even know what to think.
The kiss was amazing. but--

109
00:06:16.292 --> 00:06:18.877
What about Juliana? And Praveena?

110
00:06:18.878 --> 00:06:20.003
Exactly.

111
00:06:20.004 --> 00:06:25.425
I feel horrible about Juliana.
and I like Praveena. I really do. But--

112
00:06:25.426 --> 00:06:28.553
That is why you wrote that letter.
So you wouldn't get into a mess like this.

113
00:06:28.554 --> 00:06:31.139
But this changes everything.

114
00:06:31.140 --> 00:06:32.766
- Oh my God! Who--
- It's okay.

115
00:06:32.767 --> 00:06:34.059
He's... he's with me.

116
00:06:34.060 --> 00:06:36.144
It's okay. We're good.
Yeah.

117
00:06:36.145 --> 00:06:38.188
You brought Jin?

118
00:06:38.189 --> 00:06:40.399
You know that
Dae and Min Ho hate him. right?

119
00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.943
Okay. let's not throw stones. chaos queen.

120
00:06:42.944 --> 00:06:46.279
Jin's family has a place nearby.
and he'll be gone by the morning.

121
00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:48.324
- Min Ho and Dae. none the wiser.
- Hey. Kitty.

122
00:06:48.908 --> 00:06:49.909
Hi.

123
00:06:52.453 --> 00:06:54.746
Okay. I will give you guys some space.

124
00:06:54.747 --> 00:06:58.041
Hey. just... be careful.

125
00:06:58.042 --> 00:07:01.295
The way things are going. someone's
getting their heart broken this weekend.

126
00:07:05.967 --> 00:07:07.760
<i>Q is totally right.</i>

127
00:07:08.386 --> 00:07:11.431
<i>And that person could very well be me.</i>

128
00:07:17.979 --> 00:07:19.896
Wow. I'm so excited!

129
00:07:19.897 --> 00:07:22.566
I haven't been snowboarding
once yet this winter.

130
00:07:22.567 --> 00:07:23.942
I barely even slept.

131
00:07:23.943 --> 00:07:25.069
Mm. me either.

132
00:07:25.820 --> 00:07:29.906
I'm staying here. I'd much rather
read a book than risk breaking my neck.

133
00:07:29.907 --> 00:07:31.616
Is the Wi-Fi down?

134
00:07:31.617 --> 00:07:33.368
I have no bars.

135
00:07:33.369 --> 00:07:34.911
I've got bad news.

136
00:07:34.912 --> 00:07:36.872
I just popped my head outside.

137
00:07:36.873 --> 00:07:38.623
There was a blizzard last night.

138
00:07:38.624 --> 00:07:40.792
Must've knocked down the service
and the Wi-Fi.

139
00:07:40.793 --> 00:07:43.587
Bummer. But that means
great skiing. right?

140
00:07:43.588 --> 00:07:46.673
Unfortunately. no.
We're not going anywhere.

141
00:07:46.674 --> 00:07:48.717
It takes a day to clear the roads.

142
00:07:48.718 --> 00:07:50.553
So there's no way out?

143
00:07:51.220 --> 00:07:52.972
We're trapped?

144
00:08:00.855 --> 00:08:05.568
Min Ho. can't you make it
any warmer in here?

145
00:08:06.819 --> 00:08:08.988
Next Seollal. book a flight to Cebu.

146
00:08:13.242 --> 00:08:16.204
How do I turn on this fireplace?

147
00:08:18.873 --> 00:08:22.043
It's decorative. Dae.
All we can do is bundle up.

148
00:08:22.960 --> 00:08:26.838
This house is old. so the wood is warped
around those single-pane windows.

149
00:08:26.839 --> 00:08:29.509
Basically. it acts like a sieve
for the cold air outside.

150
00:08:32.386 --> 00:08:34.847
You thought
I was rich and dumb?

151
00:08:35.932 --> 00:08:37.892
I'll give you a pass 'cause you're cute.

152
00:08:40.728 --> 00:08:42.897
- I should wake up Q.
- No.

153
00:08:43.689 --> 00:08:46.775
He went to bed very late.

154
00:08:46.776 --> 00:08:49.320
I heard the toilet flush.
like. 1.000 times.

155
00:08:51.781 --> 00:08:55.367
Guys. what are we supposed to do
stuck here all day with no Wi-Fi?

156
00:08:55.368 --> 00:08:58.370
I have no idea. but I cannot feel my toes.

157
00:08:58.371 --> 00:09:02.165
Min Ho. are you sure there's not one part
of this house that is not freezing?

158
00:09:02.166 --> 00:09:05.252
Oh my gosh. how did I forget? The hot tub!

159
00:09:05.253 --> 00:09:06.671
- You have a hot tub?
- Yes!

160
00:09:07.338 --> 00:09:09.382
I have to go to the bathroom.

161
00:09:09.882 --> 00:09:10.758
Just one minute.

162
00:09:13.261 --> 00:09:14.511
Have you heard of knocking?

163
00:09:14.512 --> 00:09:16.055
Have you looked outside?

164
00:09:18.015 --> 00:09:19.224
We're trapped.

165
00:09:19.225 --> 00:09:22.561
It snowed? But Jin has to go
back to his parents' place.

166
00:09:22.562 --> 00:09:24.396
Clearly. that's no longer an option.

167
00:09:24.397 --> 00:09:25.480
I don't know what to do.

168
00:09:25.481 --> 00:09:27.482
How do I act normal
when I'm surrounded by--

169
00:09:27.483 --> 00:09:28.650
Both of your girlfriends?

170
00:09:28.651 --> 00:09:30.735
In a hot tub.
And they're not my girlfriends.

171
00:09:30.736 --> 00:09:35.740
What if we distract Juliana and Praveena
so you could get a chance to talk to Yuri?

172
00:09:35.741 --> 00:09:38.118
Or be there to have your back
when things get awkward.

173
00:09:38.119 --> 00:09:39.953
Yes. that's perfect. Thank you.

174
00:09:39.954 --> 00:09:41.414
Uh. no.

175
00:09:42.331 --> 00:09:43.832
I... I mean...

176
00:09:43.833 --> 00:09:46.793
Obviously. I will help you. Kitty.
but you're not supposed to be here.

177
00:09:46.794 --> 00:09:48.420
So. can we have a minute?

178
00:09:48.421 --> 00:09:50.256
Yes. of course. Sorry.

179
00:09:53.843 --> 00:09:56.678
You don't seriously expect me
to just stay hidden in here.

180
00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:57.887
Uh. yeah.

181
00:09:57.888 --> 00:10:00.890
Min Ho and Dae hate you.
and rightfully so. You bullied them.

182
00:10:00.891 --> 00:10:03.893
And if they find out we still hook up
after your track meet sabotage.

183
00:10:03.894 --> 00:10:05.312
they'll never let me live it down.

184
00:10:05.313 --> 00:10:08.315
So. you are gonna stay here.
and I'll be right back.

185
00:10:08.316 --> 00:10:11.484
Q. hurry up. We need help
shoveling out the hot tub.

186
00:10:21.329 --> 00:10:22.370
Everything okay?

187
00:10:22.371 --> 00:10:23.831
Couldn't be better.

188
00:10:25.499 --> 00:10:26.876
Where's Stella?

189
00:10:27.376 --> 00:10:29.128
She's inside with a book.

190
00:10:31.797 --> 00:10:35.718
Uh. it's just. my shoulder hurts
from clearing all that snow.

191
00:10:36.260 --> 00:10:37.428
Oh. let me help.

192
00:10:37.970 --> 00:10:39.012
Trust me.

193
00:10:39.013 --> 00:10:40.181
Ah?

194
00:10:46.228 --> 00:10:49.189
- Okay.
- It hurts worse if you fight it.

195
00:10:52.860 --> 00:10:54.027
Hey. I meant to ask.

196
00:10:54.028 --> 00:10:56.863
Did you ever find a VCR to watch
the video from the time capsule?

197
00:10:56.864 --> 00:10:59.741
Um. yeah. I... I watched it
with Yuri before we left.

198
00:10:59.742 --> 00:11:03.161
And? Was it everything you hoped for?
Did your mom say anything about Simon?

199
00:11:03.162 --> 00:11:05.330
Well. he was actually the one filming it.

200
00:11:05.331 --> 00:11:06.289
Oh wow.

201
00:11:06.290 --> 00:11:09.459
Yeah. I mean. I found his real name
and the town that he lived in.

202
00:11:09.460 --> 00:11:11.920
- So. after this trip. I'm gonna--
- You can track him down.

203
00:11:11.921 --> 00:11:15.048
I'll come. if you want.
I am great at stalking. along with heists.

204
00:11:15.049 --> 00:11:16.841
Oh. Yuri actually said that...

205
00:11:16.842 --> 00:11:18.927
- Ah.
- Never mind.

206
00:11:18.928 --> 00:11:21.347
Um. where are Yuri
and Juliana. by the way?

207
00:11:23.057 --> 00:11:25.016
So everything is Moon branded?

208
00:11:25.017 --> 00:11:28.103
What are the chances Min Ho lured us here
to join his dad's cult?

209
00:11:28.104 --> 00:11:30.231
- We should take these outside.
- Uh...

210
00:11:30.731 --> 00:11:33.942
I was thinking that we could talk first.
since we're finally alone.

211
00:11:33.943 --> 00:11:37.821
Look. I was really pissed that you missed
my art show 'cause you were with Kitty.

212
00:11:37.822 --> 00:11:41.117
- Babe. I already told you--
- Just let me finish. okay?

213
00:11:42.868 --> 00:11:48.748
I felt... so alone when I was sent
to Oakham last semester.

214
00:11:48.749 --> 00:11:51.627
It was like my world had just stopped.

215
00:11:52.253 --> 00:11:55.965
And there you were.
making all these new friends.

216
00:11:56.966 --> 00:11:58.216
And you and Kitty got so close.

217
00:11:58.217 --> 00:12:00.969
When I came back. it just felt like
you had already replaced me.

218
00:12:00.970 --> 00:12:03.680
- Babe...
- I know it was not rational.

219
00:12:03.681 --> 00:12:06.642
And I realized that
after storming off last night.

220
00:12:07.601 --> 00:12:09.811
I've been letting
my insecurities get the best of me.

221
00:12:09.812 --> 00:12:12.940
when I could just be honest
about what's going on.

222
00:12:14.066 --> 00:12:16.860
It got to the point where I thought
that you'd cheat on me with Kitty.

223
00:12:16.861 --> 00:12:22.198
and I know that is not fair.
and I am so. so sorry.

224
00:12:22.199 --> 00:12:24.577
You don't owe me an apology.

225
00:12:25.911 --> 00:12:27.412
<i>I'm</i> sorry.

226
00:12:30.499 --> 00:12:35.713
Kitty is my friend.
but no one can ever. ever replace you.

227
00:12:37.590 --> 00:12:40.176
You have my whole heart.

228
00:12:42.136 --> 00:12:44.387
And I ruined everything.

229
00:12:44.388 --> 00:12:46.724
No. Look at me.

230
00:12:47.224 --> 00:12:51.562
Look. we're not gonna let a dumb fight
get in the way of what we have. okay?

231
00:12:53.898 --> 00:12:54.898
I love you.

232
00:12:54.899 --> 00:12:56.525
I love you too.

233
00:12:57.651 --> 00:12:58.861
Come here.

234
00:13:03.365 --> 00:13:06.701
So. the thing about
the markets in Marrakesh

235
00:13:06.702 --> 00:13:09.037
is there's always
plainclothes officers around.

236
00:13:09.038 --> 00:13:11.664
- So. I ended up--
- You could legit be a spy.

237
00:13:11.665 --> 00:13:14.167
Like. the CIA should recruit you. stat.

238
00:13:14.168 --> 00:13:15.627
Thank you.

239
00:13:15.628 --> 00:13:18.129
That's so sweet of you to say.

240
00:13:18.130 --> 00:13:20.632
- I wonder if I could kill someone.
- All right. okay.

241
00:13:22.176 --> 00:13:23.092
Hey. guys.

242
00:13:23.093 --> 00:13:24.803
- Oh. hey.
- Hi.

243
00:13:24.804 --> 00:13:26.180
- Hello.
- Hey.

244
00:13:30.935 --> 00:13:33.269
- What is happening?
- Is that Stella?

245
00:13:33.270 --> 00:13:35.313
Stella! You all right?

246
00:13:35.314 --> 00:13:37.524
I was looking for blankets.
I found him in the armoire.

247
00:13:37.525 --> 00:13:39.151
What are you doing here?

248
00:13:43.239 --> 00:13:46.282
Would you believe that he's stalking me?

249
00:13:47.368 --> 00:13:49.702
Hey. can we talk?

250
00:13:49.703 --> 00:13:50.912
Are you two...

251
00:13:52.748 --> 00:13:54.082
Okay. so look.

252
00:13:54.083 --> 00:13:57.377
We both know it was a mistake. right?

253
00:13:57.378 --> 00:14:02.048
Juliana and I had a fight. I was confused.
and we just got caught up in the moment.

254
00:14:02.049 --> 00:14:03.467
watching that video.

255
00:14:04.093 --> 00:14:05.885
Thank you for telling me how I feel.

256
00:14:05.886 --> 00:14:09.681
Come on. You're into Praveena. right?

257
00:14:11.350 --> 00:14:14.186
And I'm in love with Juliana.

258
00:14:19.149 --> 00:14:20.109
Right.

259
00:14:21.777 --> 00:14:25.531
So. can we agree that
we keep this between us? Because...

260
00:14:26.824 --> 00:14:28.993
otherwise. it's going to ruin everything.

261
00:14:33.998 --> 00:14:35.915
Can't you just
go over there and apologize?

262
00:14:35.916 --> 00:14:37.918
No. they should be over it by now.

263
00:14:44.216 --> 00:14:47.678
Lucky for you.
I was prepared for the apocalypse.

264
00:14:48.262 --> 00:14:49.096
Thanks.

265
00:14:56.437 --> 00:14:59.856
Oh my God. Guess what I found in our room.
I think it's a love letter.

266
00:14:59.857 --> 00:15:01.775
Oh. let me see.

267
00:15:02.276 --> 00:15:05.153
"When we first met. I thought
we were opposites. But then I thought.

268
00:15:05.154 --> 00:15:08.616
"What if the universe made us
partners in crime for a reason?"

269
00:15:09.617 --> 00:15:10.784
Oh my God. wait.

270
00:15:11.577 --> 00:15:13.703
Partners? Opposites?

271
00:15:14.622 --> 00:15:16.915
I think Dae wrote this for me!

272
00:15:16.916 --> 00:15:18.834
I didn't know that he felt this way.

273
00:15:19.793 --> 00:15:20.627
- Hey.
- Hey.

274
00:15:20.628 --> 00:15:22.629
I'm getting kind of worried about Kitty.

275
00:15:22.630 --> 00:15:26.299
I haven't seen her in a while.
and she keeps running off to the bathroom.

276
00:15:26.300 --> 00:15:28.843
Maybe she has your... stomach thing.

277
00:15:28.844 --> 00:15:30.845
Right. Yeah.

278
00:15:30.846 --> 00:15:32.723
- I'll go check on her.
- Thanks.

279
00:15:35.392 --> 00:15:36.726
Hey. Kitty.

280
00:15:36.727 --> 00:15:38.520
- Hi.
- Oh.

281
00:15:39.021 --> 00:15:41.648
- Hey.
- I should have known better.

282
00:15:41.649 --> 00:15:45.276
- Yuri said that--
- Hey. forget about Yuri.

283
00:15:45.277 --> 00:15:47.863
Praveena's out there.
and she really likes you.

284
00:15:49.031 --> 00:15:52.408
So what? I'm supposed to act like
this kiss didn't happen?

285
00:15:52.409 --> 00:15:54.077
Doesn't that make me a liar?

286
00:15:54.078 --> 00:15:56.914
I mean. it's not like
you guys were exclusive. right?

287
00:16:05.965 --> 00:16:07.006
Eunice. are you okay?

288
00:16:07.007 --> 00:16:08.466
I found the letter!

289
00:16:08.467 --> 00:16:09.551
What letter?

290
00:16:10.177 --> 00:16:11.386
It's okay.

291
00:16:11.387 --> 00:16:13.513
I feel the same way.

292
00:16:13.514 --> 00:16:15.974
What are you talking about?

293
00:16:15.975 --> 00:16:19.602
Dae. you can be honest with me!
Like what's written in the letter...

294
00:16:19.603 --> 00:16:21.229
"You always play it cool.

295
00:16:21.230 --> 00:16:23.231
but I wonder
if you feel what I'm feeling."

296
00:16:23.232 --> 00:16:26.317
"Even when we argue.
I feel like we're connected."

297
00:16:27.361 --> 00:16:29.237
Oh. Dae!

298
00:16:29.238 --> 00:16:32.116
Can... I see that letter?

299
00:16:32.616 --> 00:16:33.659
Uh-huh.

300
00:16:34.535 --> 00:16:35.868
It doesn't have a name on it.

301
00:16:35.869 --> 00:16:39.414
Dae. I know it's for me. Look.

302
00:16:39.415 --> 00:16:41.708
"You're so hardheaded sometimes.

303
00:16:41.709 --> 00:16:43.334
it drives me crazy."

304
00:16:43.335 --> 00:16:45.336
You're telling me
this is not how you feel?

305
00:16:45.337 --> 00:16:49.799
Eunice. I am not a writer.
I'm more of a... math person.

306
00:16:49.800 --> 00:16:51.010
Oh.

307
00:16:52.177 --> 00:16:53.303
Oh my God.

308
00:16:54.596 --> 00:16:56.306
You... didn't write it.

309
00:16:58.350 --> 00:17:00.560
Eunice. I didn't write the letter. but...

310
00:17:00.561 --> 00:17:01.561
Hmm?

311
00:17:01.562 --> 00:17:03.188
I did underestimate you.

312
00:17:04.023 --> 00:17:06.275
You're not a spoiled rich girl.
You're smart.

313
00:17:06.942 --> 00:17:08.901
And that massage
you gave me in the hot tub.

314
00:17:08.902 --> 00:17:12.531
that was the most agonizing pain
I've ever experienced.

315
00:17:13.407 --> 00:17:15.451
But I feel so much better now.

316
00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:17.911
You're more than just a very.

317
00:17:18.746 --> 00:17:20.581
very pretty face.

318
00:17:21.165 --> 00:17:22.081
So...

319
00:17:22.082 --> 00:17:25.334
Of course.
it's a little soon for love letters.

320
00:17:25.335 --> 00:17:29.256
When we get back to Seoul.
would you like to get dinner with me?

321
00:17:30.299 --> 00:17:31.550
It's a date.

322
00:17:32.134 --> 00:17:32.967
Yeah.

323
00:17:32.968 --> 00:17:36.638
Wait a minute.
if you didn't write this. whose is this?

324
00:17:38.474 --> 00:17:40.059
What are you guys talking about?

325
00:17:40.768 --> 00:17:42.602
- What is this?
- Some love letter.

326
00:17:42.603 --> 00:17:43.561
Ooh.

327
00:17:43.562 --> 00:17:45.480
Hey. do you mind if I join you?

328
00:17:45.481 --> 00:17:48.901
Not at all. I could use some help
with Moon's left cheek.

329
00:17:50.319 --> 00:17:52.195
Have you been to Lotte World?

330
00:17:52.196 --> 00:17:55.531
It's an amusement park.
I was thinking that we could go together.

331
00:17:55.532 --> 00:17:56.658
I'd love that.

332
00:18:01.622 --> 00:18:02.455
Hello.

333
00:18:02.456 --> 00:18:05.833
I'm sorry. Min Ho.
but I do not feel comfortable with this.

334
00:18:05.834 --> 00:18:10.088
We broke up ages ago.
and... Stella's a nice girl.

335
00:18:10.089 --> 00:18:12.590
You can't go around writing love letters
to old flames.

336
00:18:12.591 --> 00:18:14.175
What on earth are you on about?

337
00:18:14.176 --> 00:18:17.178
- I didn't write you a letter.
- Okay.

338
00:18:17.179 --> 00:18:19.598
It says right here.

339
00:18:20.390 --> 00:18:23.726
"You are way more than the spoiled
rich girl everybody else sees."

340
00:18:23.727 --> 00:18:26.105
Okay. duh. That is so me-coded.

341
00:18:26.688 --> 00:18:30.775
I'm very invested in my girlfriend.
thank you very much.

342
00:18:30.776 --> 00:18:32.861
Have you seen her around. by the way?

343
00:18:39.618 --> 00:18:41.953
- Do you know who wrote this?
- Wrote what?

344
00:18:41.954 --> 00:18:42.870
What?

345
00:18:44.456 --> 00:18:46.166
Maybe Yuri wrote it to me.

346
00:18:47.459 --> 00:18:50.211
Guys. I can't keep up.
but that does make a lot of sense.

347
00:18:50.212 --> 00:18:51.546
Hey. what is that?

348
00:18:51.547 --> 00:18:53.381
Kitty. did you write a letter about me?

349
00:18:53.382 --> 00:18:56.342
I had no idea you felt so strongly.
but someone found a letter.

350
00:18:56.343 --> 00:19:00.596
and I read some of it. and it sounded like
you were saying you were in love with me.

351
00:19:00.597 --> 00:19:02.057
Oh my God!

352
00:19:04.560 --> 00:19:07.812
"You helped me discover
a whole new side of myself."

353
00:19:07.813 --> 00:19:10.439
"I thought I knew everything about love."

354
00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:11.399
"After all--"

355
00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:12.567
- Give me that.
- Whoa!

356
00:19:12.568 --> 00:19:15.153
No. you wait your turn
like everybody else.

357
00:19:15.154 --> 00:19:20.033
"I thought I knew everything about love.
After all. I am a matchmaker."

358
00:19:23.787 --> 00:19:24.705
Oh my God.

359
00:19:26.540 --> 00:19:28.000
This is about Yuri.

360
00:19:29.626 --> 00:19:30.835
Why did you bring this here?

361
00:19:30.836 --> 00:19:32.628
I didn't. I swear.

362
00:19:32.629 --> 00:19:34.798
You both were acting
really weird last night.

363
00:19:36.925 --> 00:19:38.010
Something happened?

364
00:19:40.137 --> 00:19:41.638
Yuri...

365
00:19:44.057 --> 00:19:45.058
Tell me I'm wrong.

366
00:19:50.981 --> 00:19:53.025
Wait. Hey!

367
00:19:54.735 --> 00:19:57.278
I am so sorry.
That really didn't mean anything.

368
00:19:57.279 --> 00:19:59.031
Please. just leave me alone.

369
00:20:03.243 --> 00:20:04.828
So. what did happen anyway?

370
00:20:06.413 --> 00:20:07.331
We kissed.

371
00:20:08.457 --> 00:20:09.708
Right before the trip.

372
00:20:12.711 --> 00:20:14.087
You knew I was worried about this.

373
00:20:14.922 --> 00:20:18.467
You swore to me that you were over Yuri.

374
00:20:19.801 --> 00:20:23.846
I don't appreciate being brought up here
as what?

375
00:20:23.847 --> 00:20:25.598
Like... like. a backup?

376
00:20:25.599 --> 00:20:28.100
No. God. no. I like you.

377
00:20:28.101 --> 00:20:32.564
You are amazing and interesting
and probably way too cool for me.

378
00:20:33.774 --> 00:20:39.154
What happened with Yuri
was obviously a massive mistake.

379
00:20:41.615 --> 00:20:44.116
I'm really sorry. I didn't mean
for any of this to happen.

380
00:20:44.117 --> 00:20:45.117
But it did.

381
00:20:47.037 --> 00:20:49.705
I'm gonna leave
just as soon as the roads are cleared.

382
00:20:49.706 --> 00:20:51.875
But for now. I'm gonna hang in here.

383
00:20:53.418 --> 00:20:54.419
Can you go?

384
00:21:05.097 --> 00:21:06.890
What do you mean? I'm not lying.

385
00:21:12.187 --> 00:21:16.108
Min Ho. Dae.
let's finish this once and for all.

386
00:21:17.526 --> 00:21:18.693
Are you gonna fight them?

387
00:21:18.694 --> 00:21:19.736
- Dude...
- No.

388
00:21:20.946 --> 00:21:23.197
I'm gonna apologize.

389
00:21:23.198 --> 00:21:25.825
- I'm sorry I bullied you two. okay?
- No.

390
00:21:25.826 --> 00:21:28.744
A begrudging apology is not enough.

391
00:21:28.745 --> 00:21:30.497
Fine.

392
00:21:31.248 --> 00:21:32.915
You know what? Bully me.

393
00:21:32.916 --> 00:21:34.208
Then we'll be even.

394
00:21:34.209 --> 00:21:36.545
- Jin. come on.
- It just got interesting again.

395
00:21:37.170 --> 00:21:39.631
I'm serious. okay?
Bully me. I can take it. Come on.

396
00:21:40.632 --> 00:21:42.883
You have very large pores.

397
00:21:42.884 --> 00:21:44.593
You're just a B-grade student.

398
00:21:44.594 --> 00:21:48.055
Also. you picked your nose
all through fourth grade.

399
00:21:48.056 --> 00:21:50.099
And once in the library.
I saw you eat a booger.

400
00:21:50.100 --> 00:21:51.183
Ew.

401
00:21:51.184 --> 00:21:52.727
This isn't helping.

402
00:21:52.728 --> 00:21:55.062
And we all know that you are the one

403
00:21:55.063 --> 00:21:57.648
who farted on the class field trip
to the Songam Space Center.

404
00:21:57.649 --> 00:22:00.860
You... You smelled up the entire bus.

405
00:22:00.861 --> 00:22:03.279
- Jin.
- Okay. now you're just making shit up.

406
00:22:03.280 --> 00:22:06.407
Oh. admit it! And we might have a truce.

407
00:22:06.408 --> 00:22:07.783
- No. I--
- No.

408
00:22:07.784 --> 00:22:08.952
You heard the man.

409
00:22:09.453 --> 00:22:10.329
Admit it!

410
00:22:16.251 --> 00:22:18.336
Okay. fine. I admit it.

411
00:22:18.337 --> 00:22:21.048
I'm a large-pored.
booger-eating. bus-farting loser.

412
00:22:23.008 --> 00:22:24.258
That's how much I like you.

413
00:22:24.259 --> 00:22:26.345
Aww.

414
00:22:27.804 --> 00:22:30.056
- It's okay.
- I don't pick my boogers anymore.

415
00:22:30.057 --> 00:22:31.099
- Okay.
- Promise.

416
00:22:33.226 --> 00:22:34.935
The Wi-Fi's back on.

417
00:22:34.936 --> 00:22:36.187
Thank the Lord.

418
00:22:36.188 --> 00:22:37.856
Yes.

419
00:22:46.031 --> 00:22:47.657
There you are. Covey.

420
00:22:50.327 --> 00:22:53.704
The roads are open.
meaning lockdown is over.

421
00:22:53.705 --> 00:22:54.705
Great.

422
00:22:54.706 --> 00:22:58.250
Covey. come out so we can talk.

423
00:22:58.251 --> 00:22:59.419
No. thank you.

424
00:23:00.504 --> 00:23:04.174
My plan is to stay in here
until I shrivel up like a prune and die.

425
00:23:05.092 --> 00:23:06.635
Should be any minute now.

426
00:23:11.390 --> 00:23:13.308
Well. if you're not coming out.

427
00:23:14.434 --> 00:23:15.268
I'm coming in.

428
00:23:17.270 --> 00:23:19.647
As if you would ruin that designer jacket.

429
00:23:19.648 --> 00:23:20.689
What. this old thing?

430
00:23:20.690 --> 00:23:22.317
Did they break up?

431
00:23:24.778 --> 00:23:27.571
<i>♪ Now I hear that ♪</i>

432
00:23:27.572 --> 00:23:31.909
<i>♪ You couldn't get back
So you started like that. yeah ♪</i>

433
00:23:31.910 --> 00:23:33.995
<i>♪ I was all alone ♪</i>

434
00:23:34.788 --> 00:23:38.124
<i>♪ See your face on the wall ♪</i>

435
00:23:38.125 --> 00:23:40.793
<i>♪ Now I hear that ♪</i>

436
00:23:40.794 --> 00:23:42.211
<i>♪ It wasn't so bad ♪</i>

437
00:23:42.212 --> 00:23:43.879
<i>♪ And you wanna come back ♪</i>

438
00:23:43.880 --> 00:23:45.631
<i>♪ Oh. yeah ♪</i>

439
00:23:45.632 --> 00:23:48.009
<i>♪ Oh. oh ♪</i>

440
00:23:48.510 --> 00:23:50.261
<i>♪ Oh ♪</i>

441
00:23:50.262 --> 00:23:51.929
<i>♪ Oh ♪</i>

442
00:23:51.930 --> 00:23:54.890
I am a terrible. awful person.

443
00:23:54.891 --> 00:23:56.184
No. you're not.

444
00:23:56.768 --> 00:23:58.270
I've hurt a lot of people.

445
00:23:58.770 --> 00:23:59.646
Hey.

446
00:24:00.647 --> 00:24:02.107
Don't be so hard on yourself.

447
00:24:03.775 --> 00:24:06.695
It's impossible to keep
emotions like that hidden.

448
00:24:08.196 --> 00:24:09.406
Take it from me.

449
00:24:12.242 --> 00:24:17.706
Good news is that
once I admitted how I felt about you...

450
00:24:19.249 --> 00:24:20.125
I could move on.

451
00:24:22.002 --> 00:24:25.046
And... so will you.

452
00:24:27.174 --> 00:24:28.633
You're a really good friend.

453
00:24:31.428 --> 00:24:34.473
I just keep wondering
how my letter even got here.

454
00:24:35.515 --> 00:24:37.601
Q's the only person who knows about it.

455
00:24:38.977 --> 00:24:40.769
Any chance you stowed it in your suitcase?

456
00:24:40.770 --> 00:24:43.230
No. I keep it hidden
in a little box in my nightstand.

457
00:24:43.231 --> 00:24:45.442
There's no chance I brought it up.

458
00:24:46.610 --> 00:24:48.528
What are you doing out here?

459
00:24:49.905 --> 00:24:52.073
Just talking as friends.

460
00:24:56.536 --> 00:24:57.579
Stel!

461
00:25:04.127 --> 00:25:05.128
Kitty.

462
00:25:06.630 --> 00:25:07.631
You okay?

463
00:25:08.298 --> 00:25:10.634
Not really. How are you two?

464
00:25:11.718 --> 00:25:12.885
We're good.

465
00:25:12.886 --> 00:25:14.637
Min Ho. Dae. and Jin all made up.

466
00:25:14.638 --> 00:25:17.306
so Stella finding Jin
in Moon's office was a good thing.

467
00:25:20.143 --> 00:25:21.477
It was weird. Uh...

468
00:25:21.478 --> 00:25:23.812
When I heard her coming.
I hid in the armoire.

469
00:25:23.813 --> 00:25:25.689
She said she was looking for blankets.

470
00:25:25.690 --> 00:25:29.568
but she was definitely opening up
his desk drawers before she found me.

471
00:25:29.569 --> 00:25:31.154
Oh. that's...

472
00:25:32.197 --> 00:25:33.030
weird.

473
00:25:36.409 --> 00:25:39.329
<i>What would Stella be looking for
in Moon's office?</i>

474
00:25:39.955 --> 00:25:43.333
<i>And whatever she was looking for.
did she find it?</i>

475
00:25:46.002 --> 00:25:48.838
<i>If Stella can snoop. so can I.</i>

476
00:25:53.927 --> 00:25:56.262
<i>Forget Moon's office.</i>

477
00:25:56.263 --> 00:25:59.015
<i>Why the hell did Stella take my letter?</i>

478
00:26:04.062 --> 00:26:05.104
Stella?

479
00:26:05.105 --> 00:26:08.858
Before you say anything.
there's something you need to see.

480
00:26:13.780 --> 00:26:14.614
All right.

481
00:26:17.617 --> 00:26:18.534
These are...

482
00:26:18.535 --> 00:26:22.664
Report cards. birthday cards
you wrote your dad. drawings.

483
00:26:25.292 --> 00:26:28.043
I found them in his office
when I ran into Jin.

484
00:26:28.044 --> 00:26:29.461
My dad kept all of these?

485
00:26:29.462 --> 00:26:32.591
He loves you.
even if he's bad at showing it.

486
00:26:33.800 --> 00:26:35.510
And you deserve to know that.

487
00:26:37.345 --> 00:26:39.431
It's time to explain you and Kitty.

488
00:26:45.854 --> 00:26:47.606
I did have feelings for Kitty.

489
00:26:48.648 --> 00:26:49.524
And I told her.

490
00:26:50.358 --> 00:26:53.236
on the plane to LA last semester.

491
00:26:54.237 --> 00:26:55.322
She turned me down.

492
00:26:56.323 --> 00:26:57.906
It's all over now.

493
00:26:57.907 --> 00:26:58.825
I'm with you.

494
00:27:01.161 --> 00:27:04.163
Thank you for telling me the truth.

495
00:27:04.164 --> 00:27:06.291
Why didn't you tell <i>me</i> the truth?

496
00:27:10.170 --> 00:27:11.838
Dae. I can explain.

497
00:27:12.422 --> 00:27:13.340
What's going on?

498
00:27:14.424 --> 00:27:16.760
You made a move on Kitty on the plane?

499
00:27:18.803 --> 00:27:21.096
And you're supposed to be my best friend.

500
00:27:21.097 --> 00:27:24.516
I <i>am</i> your best friend. Dae. Listen to me.

501
00:27:24.517 --> 00:27:25.602
Shut up.

502
00:27:27.604 --> 00:27:30.649
I don't want to talk to you. ever again.

503
00:27:31.941 --> 00:27:32.942
We're done.

504
00:27:36.946 --> 00:27:37.989
Dae. wait!
